Luminescence
============

Luminescence is an application for generating HTML presentations from Markdown sources.


Authors
-------

Pedro Matiello <pmatiello@gmail.com>


License
-------

This package is released under the MIT License. Please read COPYING for details.


Dependencies
------------

markdown2 — http://code.google.com/p/python-markdown2/
pyyaml    — http://pyyaml.org/

Developers will also need:

nose      — http://somethingaboutorange.com/mrl/projects/nose/0.11.2/
mockito   — http://code.google.com/p/mockito-python/


References
----------

Markdown — http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/